eng.nomusiccommands: ⚠️You can't use this channel for music commands!
eng.joinSame: Join the same voice channel as me!
eng.emptyQueue: It's a little quiet here. Play something! *(Atleast for me.💕)*
eng.roomSet: Ryme Command room is already set up as:
eng.enter: Enter anything else or wait 60 seconds to cancel
eng.nRelated: Can't find related video to play. Stop playing music.
eng.err: You got me. I don't handle this case!
eng.help:
List of all avalaible commands!
> **1**. Play -> Plays a given URL or fetchs 1st youtube video! _(!play **name**)_
> **2**. Search -> Searchs top 15 youtube videos! _(!search **name**)_
> **3**. Pause -> Pause current song! _(!pause)_
> **4**. Resume -> Resume paused song! _(!resume)_
> **5**. Skip -> Skip current song! _(!skip)_
> **6**. Disconnect -> Disconnect Ryme! _(!disconnect)_
> **7**. Shuffle -> Shuffle current queue randomly! _(!shuffle)_
> **8**. Loop -> Loops current song! _(!loop)_
> **9**. Loopqueue -> Loops current queue! _(!loopqueue)_
> **10**. Queue -> Outputs current queue, with Timestamps! _(!queue)_
> **11**. Volume -> Changes the volume of Played song! _(!volume **0-100**)_
> **12**. Filter -> Applies sound filter! _(!filter **!ftypes**)_
> **13**. Autoplay -> Toggles autoplay _(!autoplay)_
> **14**. Remove - Remove song from queue! _(!remove **index**)_
> **15**. Clear -> Clears the whole queue _(!clear)_
> **16**. Move -> Move song to another positoin in queue _(!move **From Index** **To Index**)_
> **17**. Playskip -> Skip current song and play another! _(!playskip **name**)_
> **18**. Setroom -> Set the room for commands! _(!setroom **Room-Name**)_
> **19**. DJ -> Toggles DJ mode! _(!dj)_
> **20**. Ping -> Check ping! _(!ping)_
> **21**. Filter Types -> Outputs all avalaible filter types! _(!ftypes)_
> **22**. Language -> Change the language of Ryme messages! _(!lang **name**)_
> **23**. Help -> Outputs help box! _(!help)_
> **24**. Fullhelp -> Outputs full help box! _(!fullhelp)_
